{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/dev/web/http","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"4c5009a6-6de7-5ff8-953c-6b0dd7c1cde8","html":"<h1 id=\"슈퍼개발자-춤추는망고입니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%88%ED%8D%BC%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90-%EC%B6%A4%EC%B6%94%EB%8A%94%EB%A7%9D%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%85%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"슈퍼개발자 춤추는망고입니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>슈퍼개발자, 춤추는망고입니다.</h1>\n<p>( <del>춤 안춥니다.</del> )</p>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"인터넷에-대한-이해\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%ED%84%B0%EB%84%B7%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4\" aria-label=\"인터넷에 대한 이해 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인터넷에 대한 이해!</h2>\n<h1 id=\"웹의-역사와-발전-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9B%B9%EC%9D%98-%EC%97%AD%EC%82%AC%EC%99%80-%EB%B0%9C%EC%A0%84-\" aria-label=\"웹의 역사와 발전  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>웹의 역사와 발전 !</h1>\n<p><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"1991년\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1991%EB%85%84\" aria-label=\"1991년 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1991년,</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">인터넷과 HTML 이 세상에 알려지고,\n\nCERN 과 팀 버너스리는 웹과 관련된 새로운 것에 도전하는데요.</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"그-도전의-끝에-있었던-것은\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B7%B8-%EB%8F%84%EC%A0%84%EC%9D%98-%EB%81%9D%EC%97%90-%EC%9E%88%EC%97%88%EB%8D%98-%EA%B2%83%EC%9D%80\" aria-label=\"그 도전의 끝에 있었던 것은 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>그 도전의 끝에 있었던 것은,</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Original HTTP</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">바로, 인터넷이라는 세상에 처음 등장한 법,\n\n통신규약이였죠.</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"같은-해\u001c\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%99%EC%9D%80-%ED%95%B4%1C\" aria-label=\"같은 해\u001c permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>같은 해\u001c,</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">HTTP 라는 통신규약은\n\n0.9 버젼으로 최초의 문서화가 진행됐어요.</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"그리고-1995년\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%AC%EA%B3%A0-1995%EB%85%84\" aria-label=\"그리고 1995년 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>그리고, 1995년,</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">데이브 레겟이라는 사람이 이끄는 조직\n\nHTTP Working Group ( HTTP WG ) 에서</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>조작과 협상의 확장</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>메타 정보의 보강</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>메소드와 헤더 필드의 추가</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">를 통한 더 효율적인 보안 프로토콜에 대한\n\n도전을 시작하는데요.</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"다음해인-1996년\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8B%A4%EC%9D%8C%ED%95%B4%EC%9D%B8-1996%EB%85%84\" aria-label=\"다음해인 1996년 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>다음해인 1996년,</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">그들의 시도는 성공을 이뤄냈고,\n\nHTTP 의 1.0 버전이 공식적으로 등장했어요.</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"http-란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#http-%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"http 란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTTP 란?</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Hyper    : 초월\nText     : 문자\nTransfer : 통신\nProtocol : 규약</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">하이퍼 텍스트를 주고받는\n\n통신의 양식에 대한 규약이에요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">HTTP 메시지는 ASCII로 인코딩된 텍스트 정보이고,\n\n설정파일 (프록시, 서버), API (브라우저의 경우) 등\n\n임의의 사용환경에 의해 가공되어 제공되요!</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"핵심-규칙은\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B5%EC%8B%AC-%EA%B7%9C%EC%B9%99%EC%9D%80\" aria-label=\"핵심 규칙은 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>핵심 규칙은!</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">컴퓨터의 통신포트 중 80번 포트를 사용해요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">TCP (Transmission Control Protocol) 라는\n\n전송제어 규약에 의해\n\n안정적으로, 순서대로, 에러없이\n\n옥텟을 교환할 수 있어요!\n( 옥텟은 8비트 데이터의 집합체에요! )</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">UDP (User Datagram Protocol) 라는\n\n사용자 데이터그램 프로토콜에 의해\n\nURL 등의 자원요청 구문에 대한\n\n단문 메세지를 교환할 수 있어요!</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"자세히-보자면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%90%EC%84%B8%ED%9E%88-%EB%B3%B4%EC%9E%90%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"자세히 보자면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>자세히 보자면,</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">사용자,\n클라이언트 (Client) 와\n\n제공자,\n서버 (Server) 사이에서 이루어지는\n\n요청 (request) 과 응답 (response) 에 대한\n\n프로토콜 (규약) 이에요!</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"이때\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4%EB%95%8C\" aria-label=\"이때 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>이때,</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">클라이언트는 웹 브라우저,\n\n서버는 서버 컴퓨터에요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">클라이언트에서 서버에게\n\n웹페이지, 그림과 같은 정보를 요청하면,\n\n서버쪽에선 클라이언트의 요청에 맞게 응답해요!</code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/dev/web/http","tagSlugs":["/tag/web/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-06-27","description":"HTTP 에 대한 글입니다.","tags":["web"],"title":"HTTP ?","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/dev/web/http"}}}